FBIS3-59202 "drweu019__a94021" FBIS-WEU-94-019-A Document Type:Daily Report 28 January 1994 ANNEX Italy & Vatican City Holds `Cordial' Meeting With Pope BR2801124194 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1215 GMT 28 Jan 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY BR2801124194 Rome ANSAMAIL Database Language: English Article Type:BFN [Unattributed article: "Premier Chernomyrdin Meets Pope"] [Text] Vatican City, 28 Jan (ANSA) -- Russian Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin, his wife, and a delegation of Russian officials on Friday morning [28 January] were received by Pope John Paul II at the Vatican, the Holy See announced. As is customary, the Vatican did not release details of the 50-minute meeting, which was described as "cordial" by delegation members.
